### CCR-028 (AT-07) — CC Player Edit Modal
###
### 검증:
### - PATCH /players/{id} 으로 정보 갱신
### - Sitting Out 즉시/지연 적용

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 36.1 GET /players/{id} — 현재 player 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/players/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: PlayerOut, error: null }

### 36.2 PATCH /players/{id} — 메타 갱신
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/players/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Player"
}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: PlayerOut, error: null }
